text: Ján Sýkora (born September 14, 1990) is a Slovak professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC 07 Detva of the Tipsport Liga. Sýkora made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Plzeň during the 2013-14 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:HC '05 Banská Bystrica players Category:Czech ice hockey forwards Category:HC Dynamo Pardubice players Category:HC 07 Detva players Category:BK Havlíčkův Brod players Category:HC Košice players Category:HC Oceláři Třinec players Category:People from Detva District Category:HC Plzeň players
